45
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,000
 Hvala što pratite kanal.

46
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,000
 Božja riječ stari zavijet.

47
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:58,000
 Ta povijest je jako konkretna.

48
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:02,000
 Znači još nismo na razini duhovnog tumačenja.

49
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:04,000
 Da je robstvo duhovna stvar.

50
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:08,000
 Da je pravo robstvo čovjeka grijeh i tako dalje.

51
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,000
 Bog je morao postepeno se objavljivati čovjeku.

52
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:15,000
 I sa izraelskim narodom morao konkretno raditi iz jednog robstva u Egiptu.

53
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,000
 Poslije su došli.

54
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:20,000
 Ova riječ zapravo govori o kontekstu je babilonsko sužanjstvo.

55
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,000
 Nakon što su već imali hram.

56
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,000
 Nakon što su već živjeli tamo.

57
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,000
 Imali kulturu, pismo, vjeru, hram.

58
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,000
 Svečenike, kralja.

59
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:32,000
 Njihovo srce se odvratilo od gospodina.

60
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,000
 I kako je bilo u ugovoru, u savezu.

61
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:36,000
 Bog je uvijek rekao.

62
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,000
 A kad vam se srce, kad mi više ne budete slušali.

63
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:40,000
 Ja ću vas predati vašim neprijateljima.

64
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:42,000
 I tako se dogodilo.

65
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:44,000
 Došli su babilonci.

66
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,000
 Pobili su koje su pobili.

67
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:48,000
 Većinu naroda su odveli.

68
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:50,000
 ostale samo sirotinja tamo na toj zemlji.

69
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:54,000
 To je ona riječ krotki će baštiniti zemlju.

70
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:56,000
 Ali to je sad druga tema.

71
00:03:56,000 --> 00:04:02,000
 Za puno toga je ključ u Svetom pismu i u Novom Zavijetu i onome što Isus govori babilonsko sužanjstvo.

72
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:08,000
 To je jedno konkretno robstvo fizičko jednog naroda gdje su ih,

73
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:10,000
 jedan drugi narod ih je porobio.

74
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,000
 To je bio običaj u to vrijeme.

75
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,000
 Kad porobiš jedan narod, odvedeš ih lijepo u kući.

76
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:16,000
 Pa ti čuvaju, imaš besplatno babysitter,

77
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:18,000
 imaš besplatno graditelje,

78
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:20,000
 imaš besplatno učitelje,

79
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,000
 školu, neko ko ti je on.

80
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,000
 Lijepo su ti robovi i to je to.

81
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:25,000
 Onda ovaj narod u babilonskom služanstvu,

82
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,000
 već desetljećima,

83
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:28,000
 neki su možda zaboravili Jeruzalem,

84
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,000
 onda su oni govorili,

85
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,000
 nek mi se osuši desnica,

86
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,000
 to jest neću svirat gitaru,

87
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,000
 ne mogu svirat,

88
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,000
 nek mi se jezik prilijepi za nepce,

89
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,000
 neću ni pjevat,

90
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,000
 kaže,

91
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,000
 jer mislim, jer mi je jedna tuga,

92
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,000
 iznad svih mojih radostima,

93
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,000
 jedna tuga, to je Čežnja za Jeruzalemom.

94
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:50,000
 To su, vidimo, tri točke geografske,

95
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:53,000
 koje mogu tebi pomoći da mapiraš,

96
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,000
 evo, gdje si ti danas,

97
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,000
 gdje je danas tvoja duša,

98
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,000
 gdje je tvoja nutrina,

99
00:04:56,000 --> 00:05:01,000
 jer jezik nutrine je uvijek neizreciv

100
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:05,000
 nekim, ne znam, govorom egzaktnim,

101
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:07,000
 zašto postoje umjetno,

102
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,000
 zašto postoje poezija,

103
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:10,000
 zašto postoje priče, bajke, mitovi,

104
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,000
 prispodove, kriz koristi,

105
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,000
 da bi se izrazilo ono što,

106
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:16,000
 ovo neizrecivo što se događa u nutrini.

107
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,000
 Evo, onda ima jedna,

108
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,000
 Bože reči danas ti daje mapu,

109
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:20,000
 da ti vidiš gdje si,

110
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,000
 i da se možeš pomaknuti,

111
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:23,000
 ako nisi na dobrom mjestu,

112
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,000
 da možeš išći naprijed.

113
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:26,000
 Onda su tri glavne geografska položaja,

114
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,000
 evo, spomenuo sam već Babilon,

115
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:31,000
 sužanjstvo, ropstvo,

116
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:33,000
 to je situacija čovjekova,

117
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:37,000
 ono za što je čovjek stvoren je Jeruzalem,

118
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:39,000
 evo, da je svoj na svome,

119
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:42,000
 evo, pokušao bi to objasniti šta to znači,

120
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:45,000
 evo, jedna od značenja je da vlada sobom.

121
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:47,000
 I to je slatko, gorko je biti u ropstvu,

122
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:49,000
 i slatko je kad vlada.

123
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,000
 između te dvije,

124
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:53,000
 ta geografska položaja,

125
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,000
 nalazi se ogromna pustinjetina.

126
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:59,000
 I čak kad bi nas ovi pustili da idemo,

127
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,000
 to se je dogodilo kad je došao jedan kir,

128
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:03,000
 jedan njihov kraj,

129
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:05,000
 kada je pustio židovski narod da se vrati,

130
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:08,000
 evo, beshrabren sam tako će sad kroz tu pustinju,

131
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,000
 a i tu sam već sam se rodio,

132
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:12,000
 tu Babilon i sam gradio kuću,

133
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,000
 i snašao sam se i tako dalje,

134
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,000
 ono su proroci došli o hrabrit narod.

135
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:20,000
 Evo, vidimo kako ta usporedba

136
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:22,000
 može nam pomoći što se događa u našoj nutrini.

137
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,000
 I onda vidi ti danas gdje si ti opita,

138
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,000
 ova riječ te pita. Gdje si ti danas?

139
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,000
 Jesi li u Babilonu?

140
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:32,000
 Jesi li krenuo na put prema Jeruzalemu?

141
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:36,000
 Ili si se asimilirao u Babilonu i to je to, živiš?

142
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:38,000
 Ili si već u pustinji,

143
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:40,000
 ide Bog za tobom,

144
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,000
 vidiš kako miče prepreke, kako si na putu,

145
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:45,000
 kako te Bog maknuje s tvoje statike,

146
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:47,000
 gdje samo čekaš smrti, to je to.

147
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:51,000
 I vidiš da nije sve jedno kako živiš, boriš se,

148
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:55,000
 to je znak da jedan čovjek hoda prema Jeruzalemu,

149
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,000
 je kajanjena.

150
00:06:57,000 --> 00:07:01,000
 Postoji čovjek koji je zaspao u Jeruzalemu,

151
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:05,000
 u Babilonu, on se navikao na sve.

152
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:07,000
 Ništa ga više ne,

153
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:09,000
 samo ga uznamiruju možda tuđi grijesi,

154
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:11,000
 a moji me više ne uznamiruju. To je tako, to tako treba biti.

155
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:13,000
 Ono treba doći jedan glas istine,

156
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:15,000
 koji mora vikat,

157
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:17,000
 to je veličina Ivana, to je divota koji imamo,

158
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:19,000
 znak u svoj tom pismu,

159
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,000
 da Bog nije znao više što,

160
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:23,000
 kako je bio ljut na narod, kako kaže,

161
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:25,000
 doslovno kaže,

162
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:27,000
 "Bog digao nos",

163
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:29,000
 mi ne provodimo tako, ali kad se čita na hebrevski,

164
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:31,000
 "Bog je digao nos".

165
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:33,000
 I onda kad je Bog skroz digao nos,

166
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:35,000
 i nije mogao,

167
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,000
 onda kaže da više nije slao riječ,

168
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:39,000
 onda su se oni tužili,

169
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:41,000
 kako više, kaže, i proroci i svećenici

170
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:43,000
 lutaju po zemlji i ništa ne znaju.

171
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:45,000
 Kako mnogi ljudi kažu,

172
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,000
 ne znam, tamo kod nas ništa,

173
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,000
 sve suhoparno, svećenik ništa ne govori,

174
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:51,000
 najviše ni propovedi, niše, evo,

175
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:53,000
 nema više riječi,

176
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,000
 ne znam, evo, to ne ovisi samo svećeniku,

177
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,000
 nego Bog da narodu,

178
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:59,000
 koji hoće slušati, da, nekom ko hoće,

179
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:01,000
 ko govori, i meni treba, svaki dan

180
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:03,000
 govoriti, treba se izlagati

181
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,000
 istini, jer znamo da je,

182
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,000
 evo, da bi malo objasnili ovo ropstvo,

183
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:09,000
 služanstvo koje mi živimo,

184
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:11,000
 svjetimo se one Isusove riječi,

185
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:13,000
 koja kaže, "Ostanite u mojoj riječi,

186
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,000
 upoznat ćete istinu,

187
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,000
 i istina će vas osloboditi."

188
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:19,000
 Sad možemo, šta će me osloboditi?

189
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,000
 To su farizei, kada Isus govorio

190
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:23,000
 o oslobodženju, oni su rekli, ma šta, nismo mi robovi.

191
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:25,000
 To je čovjek koji živi u laži,

192
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,000
 koji je otuđen,

193
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:29,000
 i zato je došao jedan krstitelj, raskrinka to,

194
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,000
 zato je vikao, prokazivao je grijehe,

195
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,000
 nije se bojavao nikoga.

196
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:35,000
 Hralju je govorio, svi znali,

197
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:37,000
 ali svi su ono malo, evo,

198
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:39,000
 ne talasaj, nemoj izgubiti glavu,

199
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:41,000
 nemoj se zamjeriti, nemojte čas zamiriti,

200
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:43,000
 kažu istri, evo, nemoj...

201
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:45,000
 Bojimo se istine

202
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:47,000
 i bojimo se jedni i drugih.

203
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:49,000
 Bog i svoje, revnoj ljubavi za nas,

204
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:51,000
 upali ovaj oganj u srcu proroka.

205
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,000
 Sjetite se, proroka Jeremija,

206
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:55,000
 kojim se više nije dalo uopće govoriti,

207
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,000
 rekao je: neću govoriti više u tvoje ime,

208
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,000
 jer samo mi donosi probleme to,

209
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:01,000
 žele me ubiti,

210
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,000
 bacili su u jedan bunar,

211
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,000
 tamo je bio Danima,

212
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:07,000
 ali onda kaže: ali u mojim kostima

213
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:09,000
 bio je zapreten oganj

214
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:11,000
 i morao sam govoriti.

215
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:13,000
 To je Božja ljubav i ja zahvaljujem Bogu

216
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,000
 da danas, nakon 2000 godina,

217
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:17,000
 nakon Ivana Krstitelja,

218
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:19,000
 još uvijek u crkvi postoji,

219
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,000
 ne znam gdje drugo,

220
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:23,000
 postoji ovaj revnost da se meni,

221
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,000
 da se tebi kaže istina.

222
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:27,000
 Ima neke opće istine,

223
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:29,000
 ne znam, koje mi ne prihvaćamo.

224
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:31,000
 Samo sam ti ovo reći,

225
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:33,000
 da ta rečenica koju Krist kaže

226
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:35,000
 istina će vas osloboditi.

227
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,000
 Šta ona znači kad malo uđeš u nju?

228
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:39,000
 To znači da smo mi u ropstvu,

229
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:41,000
 ne zato što smo prisiljeni,

230
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:43,000
 nego to je dobrovoljno ropstvo, jer želimo biti u njemu.

231
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:45,000
 žele ostati u Babilonu.

232
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:47,000
 Ne vjeruju da tamo ima,

233
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:49,000
 to je život,

234
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,000
 to je čovjek koji gleda ponografiju

235
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:53,000
 i ne želi izaći.

236
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:55,000
 Mnogi ljudi žele izaći.

237
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:57,000
 Ne, pustiti, to je život.

238
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,000
 Potpuno izgubi dostojanstvo,

239
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,000
 rob je, ne znam,

240
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:03,000
 neko je rob gnjeva,

241
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:03,000
 neko je rob tuge,

242
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:05,000
 evo možemo nabrojiti onih osam strasti.

243
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:07,000
 vidiš da je to robstvo,

244
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,000
 odozimati dostojanstvo.

245
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:11,000
 U Nisi, stari su govorili,

246
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,000
 slatko je vladati.

247
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:15,000
 To svi možemo razumjeti kako je slatko,

248
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,000
 kad imamo neku vlast.

249
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:19,000
 Ali, obično, kad imaš neku vlast,

250
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:22,000
 a svi smo grešnici pa ne radimo dobro tu vlast,

251
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:24,000
 onda donosimo gorčinu drugima.

252
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:26,000
 Onda se on bori da on dođe na vlast,

253
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:29,000
 pa i to svaku vlast onda ispuni gorčinom,

254
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:31,000
 ali ima jedna vlast

255
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:33,000
 koja je sama slatkoća.

256
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:35,000
 Kad imaš tu vlast,

257
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:37,000
 nikoga ne ispunjaš gorčinom,

258
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,000
 a u tebi je slatkoća.

259
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,000
 Znate koja je to vlast?

260
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:41,000
 Kad imaš tu vlast,

261
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,000
 nikoga ne ispunjaš gorčinom,

262
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,000
 a u tebi je slatkoća.

263
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:48,000
 to je kad imaš vlast nad samim sobom.

264
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:52,000
 Onda promisli koliko puta si neke ljude napunio gorčinom,

265
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:54,000
 jer nisi vladao sobom.

266
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:56,000
 Koliko, čovjek kada se preljubi,

267
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:58,000
 onda gorčina u djeci,

268
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,000
 u ženi koja je prevarana,

269
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,000
 u mužu koja je prevarana,

270
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:02,000
 jer čovjek nije vladao sobom.

271
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:04,000
 Vladao neke emocije,

272
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:06,000
 požuda,

273
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:08,000
 bilo što.

274
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,000
 Ili srebroljublje vlada nama,

275
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:11,000
 ili tuga vlada s nama.

276
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:13,000
 Jedino kad čovjek vlada sa sobom,

277
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:15,000
 ne ispunja,

278
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:17,000
 ne znam, ponavljam više puta,

279
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,000
 jer i meni to dira,

280
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,000
 jedin da istina,

281
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,000
 ne ispunjam druge gorčinom,

282
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:23,000
 a u meni dolazi jedna slatkoća.

283
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,000
 Puno puta Bože reči govori o slatkoći.

284
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,000
 Kriz kaže:

285
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:27,000
 Moj Aram je sladak.

286
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,000
 Onda kaže,

287
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,000
 psalam,

288
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,000
 tvoje riječi su sladke,

289
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:32,000
 ne pcu mome.

290
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,000
 Neki nas smo na zornici čitali psalam

291
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:36,000
 Bog je sladak.

292
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:38,000
 Možda to nekom se čini nerealno,

293
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:40,000
 ali želi reći da ovaj cilj,

294
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,000
 dvije stvari prorok mora vikat.

295
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:44,000
 Mora raskrenkavati grijeh,

296
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:46,000
 mora raskrenkavati robstvo i govori čovjeku:

297
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,000
 Budalo!

298
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:48,000
 Živiš u robstvu,

299
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,000
 probudi se,

300
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:51,000
 makni se s te mrtve točke.

301
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:53,000
 Zašto tamo sjediš u svom izmetu

302
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:55,000
 i kažeš da ti je dobro,

303
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,000
 Budalo?

304
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,000
 To je vikao Ivan Trsitelj,

305
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,000
 o to vičem ja danas tebi.

306
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:00,000
 Ako te ne dira,

307
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:02,000
 ako ideš u crkvu desetljećima,

308
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:04,000
 nikad se nisi pukajao za grijehe,

309
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,000
 nikad nisi naišao na ispovjed.

310
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:07,000
 Kaže ovdje da su ispovjedali svoje grijehe.

311
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:09,000
 Govorili su ih.

312
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:12,000
 To nije izmislila crkva u srednjem vijeku.

313
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:14,000
 To je Bog nadahnu u izraelskom narodu.

314
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:16,000
 već da to put izlječenja,

315
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:18,000
 izgovori svoje grijehe.

316
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:20,000
 Kad čovjek ovog svijeta izgovara svoje grijehe,

317
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,000
 uvijek izgovara tuđe.

318
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,000
 I zato ostaje u robstvu.

319
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:24,000
 Zato ostaje u tuzi.

320
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:26,000
 Ne može upoznat slatkoću,

321
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,000
 jer to je prva stvar,

322
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:29,000
 raskrinka laži,

323
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,000
 i druga stvar,

324
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:33,000
 otkrit slatkoću koju možeš dobiti.

325
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:37,000
 Možda neko misli da to da je Bog sladak,

326
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:40,000
 ta rečenica mi odzvanja od kada smo neki nam čitali

327
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:42,000
 u psalmu na Zornici,

328
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:45,000
 možda kao neka pobožnjačka stvar.

329
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:47,000
 Padaju mi na pamet više primjera.

330
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:50,000
 Sjetite se one crnkinje.

331
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:52,000
 Stavio sam, molim vas pogledajte ako niste.

332
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:56,000
 Taj njezino iskustvo može promijeniti čovjek u život.

333
00:12:56,000 --> 00:13:00,000
 Ona crnkinja koja je bila, stavio sam tamo na moj kanal,

334
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:04,000
 zove se Makjule ili Bažiza iz Ruande.

335
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:06,000
 Preživila je pokolj, ono WC u tamo,

336
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,000
 sakrivala se mjesecima,

337
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,000
 pobili svom sjelu obitelj.

338
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,000
 Ona u toj borbi,

339
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:13,000
 unutarnjoj borbi koja je fantastično opisana,

340
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:16,000
 Boga je dao i dar da to dobro opiše,

341
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:18,000
 da bi mi mogli prepoznat sebe.

342
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:21,000
 U tome je odlučila se ić,

343
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:22,000
 napustit svoj Babilon,

344
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,000
 napustit svoje gnjev,

345
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:26,000
 ropstvo gnjevu i slijedit Krista.

346
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,000
 Ona je bila katolika,

347
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:29,000
 išla je od Malena u crkvu,

348
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,000
 čula je i ušima o tome,

349
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,000
 ali poslije Bog.

350
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,000
 Jer kad je molila OČe Naš,

351
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,000
 sjetite ko niste gledali,

352
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:36,000
 toliko je bila ljuta ove ljude,

353
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:38,000
 čula ih je tamo iza ormara,

354
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:39,000
 kako se hvale,

355
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:40,000
 kako su ubili stotine ljudi.

356
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,000
 Šta je ovo?

357
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:42,000
 Kako se neko može hvali

358
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,000
 da je ubio stotine ljudi?

359
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:46,000
 Onda je došao gnjev da ih sve pobijede.

360
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,000
 Kada je molila OČe Naš,

361
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:49,000
 oprosti nam duge naše,

362
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,000
 onda nije mogla,

363
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,000
 preskakala je tu,

364
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,000
 preskakala je taj dio,

365
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,000
 nije mogla.

366
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:56,000
 Bila je više u ropstvu,

367
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:58,000
 nego u ropstvu od straha,

368
00:13:58,000 --> 00:14:00,000
 bila je u ropstvu od gnjeva.

369
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,000
 I kaže da vam se i tijelo mijenjalo,

370
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,000
 da je glava bola,

371
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:03,000
 i da je smrdila,

372
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:05,000
 i da je kada smo u tim ropstvima,

373
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:08,000
 čovjek je manje čovjek,

374
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,000
 kad živimo gnjevo.

375
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:11,000
 Onda, ovo sam ti joj reći,

376
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:13,000
 na kraju jer je išla za Kristom,

377
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,000
 divno jezino iskustvo,

378
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:16,000
 na divan način priča,

379
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,000
 vidiš unutra,

380
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:19,000
 bez osude prema ikome,

381
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,000
 kaže kad je to sve prestalo,

382
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,000
 kad je ona izašla,

383
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:23,000
 već tamo imala velike utjehe,

384
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:25,000
 već tamo kad je rekla

385
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:28,000
 neću ostati u ovom izmetu gnjeva,

386
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:30,000
 slijediću Krista,

387
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:33,000
 slijediću moga Krista,

388
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,000
 slijediću Boga,

389
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,000
 slijediću Boga,

390
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,000
 ne želim uvrijediti Krista,

391
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,000
 kad kažem da je slon,

392
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,000
 evo ova usporenda,

393
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,000
 puno veći je,

394
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:42,000
 nego što je od mene,

395
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:44,000
 nego što je veći slon od miša,

396
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:46,000
 ali evo pošto ga je slijedila,

397
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,000
 došla je onda kaže,

398
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,000
 poslije kad je to završilo,

399
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,000
 kako je u njoj bila jedna slatkoća,

400
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:52,000
 žena koju su pobili sve,

401
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:53,000
 živi u ovu slatkoću,

402
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,000
 sve bilo kaže,

403
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:56,000
 prije nikad nisam videla bi mjesec,

404
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,000
 zahvalila sam Božem,

405
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,000
 kako je lijepo imat mjesec,

406
00:14:58,000 --> 00:15:00,000
 kako je lijepo u vas stavila ovaj vjet,

407
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,000
 pa ljudi, pa odnosi,

408
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,000
 pa neko me pozdravio,

409
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,000
 ne želi me upit,

410
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:04,000
 kako divno,

411
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,000
 kako divno,

412
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:06,000
 jedna slatkoća je bila u njoj,

413
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,000
 u molitvi imala slatkoću,

414
00:15:07,000 --> 00:15:08,000
 tamo nema u videu,

415
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:11,000
 njoj je Bog da je utješi,

416
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,000
 jer to je strašno,

417
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,000
 to je pakao,

418
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:14,000
 pobili su ti svi,

419
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,000
 sve su ti pobili,

420
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:18,000
 onda Bog je daje jednu posebnu utjehu,

421
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,000
 da je imala jednu vidženje,

422
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:21,000
 to sam čitao u knjizi,

423
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:22,000
 nema onog videu,

424
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:26,000
 vidjela je duše u blaženstvu vječnu,

425
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:28,000
 i to je isto dalo jednu snagu,

426
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,000
 da može oprostiti,

427
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:30,000
 da može,

428
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:32,000
 bilo je stvarno nešto,

429
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:33,000
 stvarno nešto,

430
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,000
 ako je išta neoprostivo,

431
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:35,000
 bilo je to,

432
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,000
 padam i na pamet,

433
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:38,000
 i Chiara Corbelo,

434
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,000
 nadam se da će biti proglašena svetom,

435
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,000
 kad je umirala,

436
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:43,000
 jer nije htjela uzeti kemoterapiju,

437
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:45,000
 pošto je bila trudna,

438
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:47,000
 nije htjela,

439
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:50,000
 ni htjela sačuvati dijete,

440
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:52,000
 onda kad je umirala nakon što je rodila,

441
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:54,000
 tumor se je raširio,

442
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:56,000
 onda je pitao muž,

443
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,000
 čak malo ljutit,

444
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,000
 malo provocirajući,

445
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,000
 bili su oboje u vjeri,

446
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:02,000
 ali on je prolazio svoje faze i ljutnije i svega,

447
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,000
 onda je pitao,

448
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:06,000
 ma ili stvarno njegov jaram sladak i breme lako,

449
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,000
 i onda mu je odgovorila,

450
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:10,000
 unutar vatre ovog trpljenja,

451
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:12,000
 kušam slatkoću njegove ljubav.

452
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:14,000
 To ne može biti nešto pobožnjački,

453
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:16,000
 to nije nešto otuđeno,

454
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:19,000
 čovjek može kušati slatkoću Bože ljubavi,

455
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,000
 može,

456
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:23,000
 danas ako vidiš da te ispunja gorčinom ovo,

457
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:25,000
 da si u Babilonu, u ropstvu, u sužanstvu,

458
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:28,000
 poslušaj danas ovaj glas istine,

459
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:30,000
 jako je važno izlagat se istini,

460
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:32,000
 jako je važno što ti gledaš na Youtube,

461
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:34,000
 jako je važno što ti čitaš,

462
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:37,000
 da li samo stojiš ispred televizije i gledaš laži,

463
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:41,000
 slušaš laži ili čemu izlažeš svoje uši?

464
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:43,000
 Čuvaj svoje uši,

465
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:45,000
 preko njih nas je,

466
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:47,000
 sva zla ovog svijeta su došla preko uši,

467
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:49,000
 preko misli, preko slušanja.

468
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:51,000
 I to izgleda nešto simpatično,

469
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,000
 Adam je evo,

470
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:54,000
 gledaj kako simpatično ovaj plot zabranjeni,

471
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:56,000
 evo iz tog simpatičnog neposluha,

472
00:16:56,000 --> 00:16:58,000
 svi kont slogori, sva pedofilija,

473
00:16:58,000 --> 00:17:00,000
 sav užas ovog svijeta proizlazi,

474
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:02,000
 a mi nismo toga bili svjesni.

475
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:04,000
 To je jako važno,

476
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:06,000
 početi izlagati svoje uši istini,

477
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:08,000
 tražiti istinu,

478
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:10,000
 i početi govoriti istinu.

479
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:11,000
 Evo potičem te danas,

480
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:12,000
 da trajiš gospodina,

481
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:13,000
 da ti da,

482
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:14,000
 da možeš,

483
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:17,000
 uvijek kada je početak obračina nekog čovjeka,

484
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:19,000
 kada jedan čovjek se pomakao

485
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:22,000
 sa ove mrtve točke svog sužajnstva,

486
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:25,000
 jedan od prvih koraka je dobra ispovjede.

487
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:27,000
 Imao sam milost zadnjih mjeseci,

488
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:28,000
 slušat dobre ispovjede.

489
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,000
 Kad dođe,

490
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,000
 nema filozofije,

491
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:32,000
 samo ti čovjek dođe i kaže,

492
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:34,000
 jesam, to sam, to sam, to sam,

493
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,000
 ja vam kažeš,

494
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:36,000
 Bog te ljubi, brate,

495
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:39,000
 tješite moj narod,

496
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:41,000
 govorite da je moj ropstvo dokončano,

497
00:17:41,000 --> 00:17:43,000
 nema nikakve osude,

498
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:46,000
 samo zamisliš šta je dovoljno

499
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:49,000
 za početi izlaziti iz ovog ropstva

500
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:51,000
 i početi već kušati,

501
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:53,000
 predokus ove slatkoće Božije,

502
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,000
 priznat,

503
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,000
 početi govoriti istinu.

504
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:57,000
 A istina je jednostavna,

505
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:59,000
 istina nije komplicirana.

506
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:00,000
 evo, recimo,

507
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:01,000
 jedna opća istina,

508
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:03,000
 koju malo ko,

509
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:05,000
 koju malo ko prihvaća,

510
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,000
 jer nam je gorka,

511
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:07,000
 nam se čini,

512
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:08,000
 a to je,

513
00:18:08,000 --> 00:18:09,000
 da mi umiremo,

514
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:10,000
 da ti danas možeš umri,

515
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:12,000
 da nemaš nikakvu sigurnost u životu,

516
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,000
 da pred smrću,

517
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:15,000
 sve što mi radimo na ovom svijetu,

518
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:17,000
 ko nije usmireno na Boga,

519
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:19,000
 da je sve besmisleno.

520
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:21,000
 I koliko ljudi prihvaća tu činjenje,

521
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:22,000
 to je istina.

522
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:23,000
 kako se branim,

523
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:24,000
 nemojte biti tako pesimistični,

524
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:26,000
 pa ja radim za svoju djecu,

525
00:18:26,000 --> 00:18:28,000
 i tvoja djeca će umrijeti,

526
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:29,000
 tvoja djeca će se, evo,

527
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:30,000
 moram govoriti istinu,

528
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:31,000
 kao imam krstitelj,

529
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,000
 će se raspadati u grobu,

530
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:34,000
 poješe ih crvi.

531
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:36,000
 I njihovu djecu ako budu imali,

532
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:37,000
 i ne znam,

533
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:40,000
 a danas moramo govoriti i o zbiljnije stvari,

534
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:41,000
 i reći,

535
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:43,000
 imamo moja djeca,

536
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:44,000
 gledamo u Istriju,

537
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:46,000
 evo, ljudi imaju ta dva sina,

538
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,000
 jedan je,

539
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,000
 sad puno primjera,

540
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:49,000
 ne mislim sad neko,

541
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:50,000
 jedan je homoseksualac,

542
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:51,000
 drugi,

543
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:53,000
 nema nikakvog smisla da ima djecu,

544
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:54,000
 još su sada,

545
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:56,000
 iznajemljuju sve živo,

546
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:57,000
 jer ih je malo,

547
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:59,000
 njih naslijedilo puno,

548
00:18:59,000 --> 00:19:00,000
 sad kad oni umru,

549
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:01,000
 evo, ko će to,

550
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:03,000
 čije li će to biti,

551
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:04,000
 Jezus Hristo onome što je rekao,

552
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,000
 večera će se tvoja duša,

553
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:06,000
 to je stvarno,

554
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,000
 znači,

555
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:08,000
 a nemojte biti tako pesimistici,

556
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:10,000
 to je naše opiranje istini,

557
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:12,000
 prihvati ovu gorku istinu,

558
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:13,000
 da je život besmislen,

559
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:14,000
 i da ti umireš,

560
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:18,000
 i vidjet ćeš malo pomalo kako se otvaraš smislu,

561
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:19,000
 pravom smislu,

562
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:20,000
 ne lažnom smislu,

563
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,000
 koji je laž,

564
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:25,000
 koji je skrivanje sebi istine,

565
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:27,000
 ili recimo jedna pojedinačna istina,

566
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:28,000
 osobna istina,

567
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:30,000
 to da sam ja grešnik,

568
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:31,000
 to da sam ja,

569
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,000
 ne onako,

570
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:33,000
 a svi smo mi grešnici,

571
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:34,000
 znate velje často,

572
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:35,000
 svi mi griješimo,

573
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:37,000
 nego prihvatit stvarno svog života,

574
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,000
 da sam jadan,

575
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,000
 ovo ja kaže vama,

576
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:40,000
 ja,

577
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,000
 vaš župnik,

578
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:42,000
 sam jadan,

579
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:45,000
 koliko puta glumim nekog dobrotvora,

580
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:46,000
 glumim nešto,

581
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:47,000
 prihvatit tu istini,

582
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:47,000
 kaže,

583
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:48,000
 da su dolazili Ivanu

584
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,000
 i priznavali su to,

585
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,000
 ja sam,

586
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:51,000
 evo,

587
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:53,000
 do tada su glumili dobrotvore,

588
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:54,000
 rekli su,

589
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:55,000
 ja sam lopo,

590
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:56,000
 ja sam ukrao,

591
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:57,000
 a nisam ja ukrao,

592
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:58,000
 aj malo promisli,

593
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:59,000
 vidi ćeš,

594
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:01,000
 koliko krađa u svom životu,

595
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:02,000
 kaže,

596
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:03,000
 nisam,

597
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:04,000
 i kaže,

598
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,000
 ja sam umišljen,

599
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:06,000
 a nisam ja,

600
00:20:06,000 --> 00:20:07,000
 nikada sam pričao s jednim mladićem,

601
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:09,000
 onda sam počeo malo ono,

602
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:10,000
 u buntu,

603
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,000
 to je najnormalnija stvar,

604
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,000
 da djete je u buntu,

605
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,000
 u tim godinama,

606
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:14,000
 ali taj buntu,

607
00:20:14,000 --> 00:20:16,000
 može ići u dobrom smjeru,

608
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,000
 to je u samostaljenje od roditelja,

609
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:19,000
 može ići u glupom smjeru,

610
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:20,000
 ovaj mladić za sada,

611
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:22,000
 za sada ide u glupom smjeru,

612
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:24,000
 onda smo govorili o umišljenosti,

613
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:24,000
 on rekao,

614
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:25,000
 nisam ja umišljen,

615
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:26,000
 ja nisam umišljen.

616
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:28,000
 Svaka rečenica koja je rekao,

617
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,000
 bila je umišljenost.

618
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:32,000
 Kad nekos 15 godina misli da je popio su pamet svijeta,

619
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:33,000
 da on zna,

620
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:35,000
 da su njegove roditelji glupi,

621
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,000
 sve je umišljeno u njemu,

622
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,000
 sve je umišljeno,

623
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:38,000
 ali on kaže,

624
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,000
 nisam umišljen,

625
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:40,000
 kako može,

626
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:42,000
 negdje će morati udrit glavom u zid.

627
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:44,000
 Bogu hvala kada kaže,

628
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,000
 jesam,

629
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:46,000
 umišljen sam.

630
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:48,000
 To je početak izlaska

631
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:49,000
 iz tih laži,

632
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:50,000
 iz tog robstva,

633
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:52,000
 prema slatkoći za koje nas je stvorio Bog.

634
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:54,000
 Diram još ovaj riješ slatkoća,

635
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:56,000
 jer znamo da se mi tješimo,

636
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:57,000
 kad malo smo u depri,

637
00:20:57,000 --> 00:20:59,000
 već je od milja zovemo depra,

638
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:01,000
 onda šime se tješimo,

639
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:02,000
 šime se tješite,

640
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:03,000
 posebno žene,

641
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:04,000
 malo sladoleda,

642
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:05,000
 malo čokolade,

643
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:06,000
 malo nutelle,

644
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:08,000
 slatkoća nam treba.

645
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:10,000
 Neki ozbilnije idu neku slatkoću

646
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:11,000
 i heroinima kažu,

647
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:13,000
 Bogu hvala da nisam probao nikad drogu,

648
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:14,000
 ali ono što mi kaže,

649
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:16,000
 da ima jednu slatkoću strašnu,

650
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,000
 koja te,

651
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:18,000
 evo ali,

652
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,000
 sjetite se što kaže,

653
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:21,000
 slatkoća kao utjeha,

654
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:23,000
 onda puno Boža riješ govori o utjesi,

655
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:25,000
 i kaže,

656
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:26,000
 jao vama,

657
00:21:26,000 --> 00:21:27,000
 već imate svoju utjehu,

658
00:21:27,000 --> 00:21:29,000
 kaže Bogatašima,

659
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:31,000
 a kaže salmista,

660
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:32,000
 kad je spoznao slatkoću Božju,

661
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:33,000
 kaže,

662
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:35,000
 utjehu odklanja duša moja,

663
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:37,000
 kad malo spoznaš utjehe Božje,

664
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,000
 milosrđe,

665
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:39,000
 njegovu ljubav,

666
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:40,000
 biti u njegovoj milosti,

667
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:41,000
 kako je to slatko,

668
00:21:41,000 --> 00:21:42,000
 kako je to lipo,

669
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:43,000
 kako ti je Bog brati dostojamstvo,

670
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,000
 pa možeš reći,

671
00:21:44,000 --> 00:21:46,000
 ne onim stvarima koji te ponižavaju,

672
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:47,000
 možeš vladat sa sobom,

673
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:48,000
 kako je lipo,

674
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:51,000
 tada možeš otklanjati lažne utjehe,

675
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,000
 utjehe slatkoću,

676
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:54,000
 slatkoću,

677
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,000
 a može tako nazvat slatkoću grijeha,

678
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:58,000
 kažu da svi grijezi nose u sebi jedan otrov slatkoća,

679
00:21:58,000 --> 00:21:59,000
 osim jednog grijeha,

680
00:21:59,000 --> 00:22:01,000
 svi znate koji je to grijeh,

681
00:22:01,000 --> 00:22:03,000
 koji nema u sebi nikakve slatkoće,

682
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:04,000
 to je prvi od svih grijeha,

683
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:05,000
 to je misteri,

684
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:07,000
 kako je došlo zlo na svijet,

685
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,000
 kažu da prvo je zavisti,

686
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:10,000
 ona u sebi nema nikakvu slatkoću,

687
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:12,000
 svi drugi grijezi nose nešto,

688
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:14,000
 u njoj se samo mučiš,

689
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:16,000
 ali to je slatkoća mišolovke,

690
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:18,000
 one pancete koje te zarobi,

691
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:19,000
 utjehu,

692
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:21,000
 tu slatkoću odbacuje duša moja,

693
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:23,000
 blago onom koje to u sebi govori,

694
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:24,000
 ne želim to,

695
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,000
 želim pravu utjehu,

696
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:26,000
 Božio,

697
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:29,000
 to je došašljena spoziva na iščekivanje toga,

698
00:22:29,000 --> 00:22:30,000
 na borbu za tim,

699
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:31,000
 i zašto,

700
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:32,000
 sad imam,

701
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:33,000
 meni puno pomažu zornice,

702
00:22:33,000 --> 00:22:34,000
 dizanje ujutro,

703
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,000
 vidio sam i drugima,

704
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:36,000
 danas,

705
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:38,000
 neki su mi rekli da osjećam blizinu neba,

706
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:40,000
 ujutro kad pjevamo psalame,

707
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:42,000
 kada zajedno molimo,

708
00:22:42,000 --> 00:22:43,000
 kada,

709
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:45,000
 posebno ujutro kad nas ništa ne smeta,

710
00:22:45,000 --> 00:22:46,000
 nema strke,

711
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:47,000
 nema telefona,

712
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:49,000
 nema ova slatkoća divna,

713
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:51,000
 zašto od nas crkva više potiče,

714
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:53,000
 i u molitvi mi tražimo ovu slatkoću,

715
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:55,000
 ne neku otuđenu slatkoću,

716
00:22:55,000 --> 00:22:56,000
 nego pravu slatkoću,

717
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:58,000
 slatkoću Jeruzalema,

718
00:22:58,000 --> 00:23:00,000
 slatkoću Kristove blizine,

719
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:03,000
 koja nas potiče da izađemo

720
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:04,000
 iz lažne,

721
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:06,000
 otrovne slatkoće Babilona.

722
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:07,000
 Amen.

